Packages 
Package Description
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification
It contains the main classes of the library.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.constants
It contains project constants
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.dao
It contains Data Access Object (DAO) from the project
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.entity
It contains the library entitys.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.enumarator
It contains the enums.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.exception
It has the library exceptions.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.gcm
It contains the classes that implement the Gcm (push notification service) by Google.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.http
It contains the classes responsible for Http requests the library.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.interfaces
It contains the library listeners.
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.service
It contains service classes that perform the treatments of the required information from the server
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.task
It contains the classes that create threads and are used in service classes
br.com.allin.mobile.pushnotification.webview
The classes of this package are responsible for implementing the WebView with the HTML campaign.
